DISCLAIMER — NOT INVESTMENT ADVICE

This software is provided for informational and educational purposes only and
does not constitute investment, financial, or trading advice. Options-market
metrics (GEX, DEX, VEX/Vanna, Max Pain, Expected Move, Put/Call ratios, walls,
switch points) are derived from a user-supplied CSV and rely on modeling
assumptions about dealer positioning that may not reflect actual market
positioning. Parsed values (spot price, timestamp, expirations) may be stale or
incorrect. Nothing here is a recommendation to buy or sell any security. Use at
your own risk; verify all figures independently before making any decision.
